description: The STOXX Europe 600 Index aims to reflect the performance of the following market: Large, mid and small-cap companies from Developed European countries 600 largest and most liquid companies Weighted by free-float adjusted market capitalisation Quarterly index review, largest component is capped at 20% Additional information on the index, selection and weighting methodology is available at https://www.stoxx.com
